Satellite erp installation roll up from 1st nov

We will begin installation of the new on-board unit (#OBU) under the#ERP2.0 system in phases  starting with fleet vehicles (i.e. those which are registered to either a company or an organisation)  from 1 Nov 2023.For individual vehicle owners  we will inform you to install the OBU when it’s your turn. New vehicles will undergo OBU installation first  while the remaining vehicles will be scheduled in batches based on their age. Instructions will be provided and more details will be available in Q1 2024.Check out the above to find out more.
